/root/sparsify-ascend/research/history/logs/agent_action_0105.json:1:{"change_type":"edit_sae_code","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"LATENTS_PER_EXPERT","value":"512"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"shared_routed_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_shared(x)} α_i^sh(x) b_i^sh + Σ_{e∈E(x)} Σ_{j∈S_e(x)} α_{e,j}(x) b_{e,j}，其中 B^sh 是始终激活的静态 shared 子库，E(x) 是轻量 router 选出的少量 routed experts，所有原子都来自静态向量库，因此在线侧仍可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“shared 子库查表 + routed 子库查表 + 有限加权和”链路，兼容性判断为直接兼容。唯一主假设：r103→r104 已证明 shared+routed 路线存在真实容量收益，但继续只扫 `NUM_EXPERTS=32->64->128` 的信息增量开始下降；更关键的问题是，在保持总静态容量扩张的同时，把每个 expert 变窄是否能把 active path 成本压回更低成本带。由于当前 `EXPANSION_FACTOR` 不能表达 `EF<1`，本轮先做最小工程接线，引入显式 tunable `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT`，并相对 r104 只新增这一个 env 参数 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=512` 做首轮生效验证。如果该参数真实进入 round config / checkpoint config，且窄 expert 版本在更低选择成本下仍保持可用 FVU，则下一轮再做 operator guide 指向的 matched-cost `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` 结构实验。","needs_sanity":true,"next_hypotheses":["如果 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=512` 生效且结果仍有竞争力，下一轮相对本轮只改 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`，做 operator guide 指定的 matched-cost shared+routed probe。","如果参数已生效但 FVU 明显崩塌，说明 shared+routed 当前收益更依赖单 expert 宽度而非更细粒度路由，后续不应继续在这条 family 上强推多 active experts。","如果 `512` 过窄，可在保持 family 与其余配方不变的前提下只改 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=768`，定位 shared+routed 的宽度 knee。"],"notes_to_memory":["已新增 tunable `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT`，并接通 `sparsify/`、`research/AutoResearch/`、`scripts/autoresearch_test.sh` 的最小必要链路；`shared_routed_expert_topk` 等 expert family 现在可以显式控制 per-expert width。","本地接线自检已通过：`validate_env_overrides` 不再拒绝 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT`；shared_routed_expert_topk 在 `K=128, EF=1, NUM_EXPERTS=64, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=512` 下 forward/backward smoke 通过。","已完成首轮参数生效验证：本地 runner 生成的 round config JSON 与 TrainConfig 持久化出的 checkpoint config JSON 中都出现 `latents_per_expert=512`，且 reference_round=104 继承的 `num_experts=64` 仍正确保留。","resume/validation 路径也已补齐：`sparsify/__main__.py` 的 resume signature 现在包含 `latents_per_expert`，避免后续 resume 校验静默漏掉该参数。"],"reference_round":104,"self_review":"这轮先修复了 r105 的真实 blocker，而不是把 `Disallowed env override keys: LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 误判成结构结论。相对 r104 的实验语义仍只新增一个 env 参数 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT`，满足单变量原则；代码改动也限制在允许范围内的 `sparsify/`、`research/AutoResearch/`、`scripts/autoresearch_test.sh`。我已做本地验证，确认新 key 进入 override allowlist、runner runtime config、checkpoint config 和 resume signature，不会在训练启动前再次被判为 disallowed。","summary":"已实际落盘 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 的端到端接线，并完成本地验证：新参数可被 AutoResearch 接受，expert family 可消费该宽度，`shared_routed_expert_topk` 的 round config / checkpoint config 都能正确记录 `latents_per_expert=512`。建议本轮以 r104 为 reference，只加 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=512`，先拿到“更窄 per-expert width”这条 high-information low-cost 方向的首个有效训练点。","touched_files":["sparsify/__main__.py","sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py","research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py","research/AutoResearch/config_resolution.py","research/AutoResearch/controller.py","research/AutoResearch/policy.py","research/AutoResearch/prompt.py","research/AutoResearch/runner.py","research/AutoResearch/rebuild_runtime_state.py","research/AutoResearch/audit_history_execution.py","scripts/autoresearch_test.sh"]}
/root/sparsify-ascend/research/history/round_summaries/round_0069.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u4fdd\u6301\u4e3a x_hat = \u03a3_e \u03a3_{i\u2208S_e(x)} \u03b1_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}\uff0c\u5176\u4e2d e(x) \u7531\u8f7b\u91cf router \u9009\u51fa\u5355\u4e2a expert\uff0c{B_e} \u662f\u9759\u6001 expert \u5b50\u5e93\u3002\u5728\u7ebf\u4fa7\u53ef\u76f4\u63a5\u5bfc\u51fa\u4e3a LUTurbo/Lottable \u7684\u201crouter \u9009\u9759\u6001\u5b50\u5e93 + \u5b50\u5e93\u5185\u67e5\u8868 + \u6709\u9650\u52a0\u6743\u548c\u201d\u63a8\u7406\u94fe\u8def\uff0c\u4e0d\u4f9d\u8d56\u52a8\u6001\u751f\u6210\u5b57\u5178\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64\u517c\u5bb9\u6027\u5224\u65ad\u4e3a\u76f4\u63a5\u517c\u5bb9\u3002\u552f\u4e00\u4e3b\u5047\u8bbe\uff1a\u76f8\u5bf9 r68 \u4ec5\u628a K \u4ece 192 \u964d\u5230 160\uff0c\u5728\u4fdd\u6301 ARCHITECTURE=expert_topk\u3001NUM_EXPERTS=32\u3001EF=1\u3001ACTIVE_EXPERTS=1 \u4e0d\u53d8\u65f6\uff0c\u5982\u679c r68 \u7684\u6536\u76ca\u6765\u81ea routed-only MoE-like \u5b50\u5e93\u5bb9\u91cf\u786e\u5b9e\u66f4\u5339\u914d\u5f53\u524d target\uff0c\u800c\u4e0d\u53ea\u662f\u4f9d\u8d56\u8f83\u5927\u7684\u67e5\u8868\u9884\u7b97\uff0c\u90a3\u4e48\u8be5 family \u5e94\u80fd\u5728\u66f4\u4f4e total_cost \u4e0b\u4fdd\u7559\u5927\u90e8\u5206\u8d28\u91cf\uff0c\u4ece\u800c\u628a\u8fd9\u6761\u76f4\u63a5\u517c\u5bb9\u7684 routed-only \u524d\u6cbf\u5411\u5de6\u5ef6\u4f38\u3002",
