/root/sparsify-ascend/research/history/logs/agent_action_0100.json:1:{"command":"run","change_type":"param_only","reference_round":99,"family_name":"lowrank_expert_residual","family_stage":"mainline","experiment_tier":"full","expected_win":"lower_fvu","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"K","value":"128"}],"hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x-t(x))}(x-t(x))} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i} + Σ_{j∈S_2(r_1)} γ_j(x) c_j，其中 t(x)=Σ_r β_r(x)u_r 是共享 low-rank trunk，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库，r_1 = x - t(x) - Σ_{i∈S_{e(x-t(x))}(x-t(x))} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}，C={c_j} 是静态 residual 补偿库。在线侧仍可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“trunk 查表 + 单个静态 expert 子库查表 + residual 补偿查表 + 有限加权和”推理链路，因此 `lowrank_expert_residual` 属于扩展兼容；`expert_topk` 属于直接兼容；`batch_topk` / `adaptive_budget_topk` 属于不兼容，不能驱动 frontier。唯一主假设是：r98 在 `K=96`、r99 在 `K=112` 上连续给出清晰正斜率，说明当前压缩版三段式结构仍然受 deployment lookup budget 限制，而不是已经在 `K=96` 附近饱和。相对 r99 仅将 `K: 112 -> 128`，在保持 `TRUNK_RANK=40`、`NUM_EXPERTS=32`、`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`OPTIMIZER=adam`、`LR=8e-4` 不变时，如果这条 family 的收益继续随 K 增长，那么 FVU 应进一步低于 r99 的 0.0973，并完成当前 `lowrank_expert_residual` deployment knee 的上沿定位。","summary":"r98 和 r99 已经把压缩版 `lowrank_expert_residual` 从 `K=96` 推到 `K=112` 且持续改善，因此本轮不切 family，也不回到 `lowrank_expert_topk` 或 routed-only 方向。以 r99 为 reference，只改 `K=128`，直接回答这条三段式主线在当前 recipe 下的 deployment budget 是否仍有显著质量收益，并完成 `K=96-128` 的上沿定位。","self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r99 只改 `K`。这不是旧 family 的盲目 K 轴细扫，而是在连续两轮正信号后，对当前最有希望的中低成本三段式主线做一次必要的上沿确认。选择 `128` 而不是先改 `STAGE1_RATIO`，是因为当前最清楚的未决问题仍是 lookup budget 斜率是否继续存在；若 r99 已接近饱和，这轮会直接给出答案。主要风险是 FVU 改善很小而成本继续上升，但这同样有价值，因为它会告诉我们后续该把预算转向预算重分配或新 family，而不是继续堆 K。","touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["r98 (`lowrank_expert_residual K=96 TRUNK_RANK=40 NUM_EXPERTS=32`) 到 r99 (`K=112`) 给出连续正斜率，说明当前压缩版三段式结构的收益不只来自 residual 是否存在，也仍受 deployment budget 影响。","当前最有信息量的问题是 `lowrank_expert_residual` 在这套压缩 recipe 下的 K-knee 上沿，而不是继续回到 `lowrank_expert_topk` 做局部补点。","按当前 fresh cost 估算，`lowrank_expert_residual K=128 TRUNK_RANK=40 NUM_EXPERTS=32 STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 仍明显低于 1.5×h×n 硬预算，并处于允许的中低成本结构对照带。","当前不要把 `expert_topk ACTIVE_EXPERTS>1` 的负信号外推到 future shared+routed-expert family；但在现有 family 仍有清晰单变量正斜率时，也不应提前切去 code-edit。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `K=128` 继续明显优于 r99，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `STAGE1_RATIO`，测试在已确认更高 K 有效后，expert 段与 residual 段的最优预算分配。","如果 `K=128` 只带来极小改善，则说明这条 family 在当前压缩 recipe 下的 deployment knee 已接近 `K=112`；下一轮应停止继续堆 K，转而测试 `STAGE1_RATIO` 或准备 shared+routed-expert 新 family。","如果 `K=128` 意外退化，则说明 r98-r99 的收益更可能来自较低 K 正则化或训练噪声；下一轮应回到 `K=112`，并优先做同 family 的预算重分配验证而不是继续上探。"]}
/root/sparsify-ascend/research/history/round_summaries/round_0097.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u4fdd\u6301\u4e3a x_hat = \u03a3_{r=1..R} \u03b2_r(x) u_r + \u03a3_{i\u2208S_{e(x-t(x))}(x-t(x))} \u03b1_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}\uff0c\u5176\u4e2d t(x)=\u03a3_r \u03b2_r(x)u_r\uff0cU={u_r} \u662f\u9759\u6001 low-rank trunk \u5411\u91cf\u5e93\uff0c{B_e} \u662f\u9759\u6001 expert \u5b50\u5e93\uff0ce(\u00b7) \u662f\u8f7b\u91cf router \u9009\u51fa\u7684\u5355\u4e2a expert\u3002\u5728\u7ebf\u4fa7\u4ecd\u53ef\u76f4\u63a5\u5bfc\u51fa\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u7684\u201ctrunk \u67e5\u8868 + \u5355\u4e2a\u9759\u6001 expert \u5b50\u5e93\u67e5\u8868 + \u6709\u9650\u52a0\u6743\u548c\u201d\u63a8\u7406\u94fe\u8def\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64 `lowrank_expert_topk` \u5c5e\u4e8e\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9\uff1b`expert_topk` \u5c5e\u4e8e\u76f4\u63a5\u517c\u5bb9\uff1b`batch_topk` / `adaptive_budget_topk` \u5c5e\u4e8e\u4e0d\u517c\u5bb9\uff0c\u4e0d\u80fd\u9a71\u52a8 frontier\u3002\u552f\u4e00\u4e3b\u5047\u8bbe\u662f\uff1ar95 (`K=128`) \u4e0e r96 (`K=96`) \u5df2\u7ecf\u628a\u5f53\u524d\u6709\u6548\u4e3b\u7ebf `lowrank_expert_topk` \u7684 deployment-knee \u4e24\u7aef\u90fd\u6d4b\u51fa\u6765\uff0c\u4f46\u4e2d\u95f4\u7f3a\u5c11 `K=112` \u8fd9\u4e2a\u6700\u5173\u952e\u7684\u8fb9\u754c\u70b9\u3002\u76f8\u5bf9 r95 \u4ec5\u5c06 `K: 128 -> 112`\uff0c\u5728\u4fdd\u6301 `TRUNK_RANK=40`\u3001`NUM_EXPERTS=32`\u3001`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`\u3001`OPTIMIZER=adam`\u3001`LR=8e-4` \u4e0d\u53d8\u65f6\uff0c\u5982\u679c\u5f53\u524d\u8d28\u91cf\u9000\u5316\u4e3b\u8981\u53d1\u751f\u5728 `K<112` \u4e4b\u540e\uff0c\u90a3\u4e48 `K=112` \u5e94\u80fd\u660e\u663e\u4f18\u4e8e r96 \u7684 0.1305\uff0c\u540c\u65f6\u628a total_cost \u4ece r95 \u7684\u540c\u914d\u65b9\u8fdb\u4e00\u6b65\u5de6\u79fb\u5230\u7ea6 0.43x\uff08\u6309\u5f53\u524d fresh cost \u7c97\u4f30\uff09\uff0c\u4ece\u800c\u5b8c\u6210 `K=96-128` \u8fb9\u754c\u5b9a\u4f4d\u3002",
