/root/sparsify-ascend/research/history/logs/agent_round_0105.stdout.log:11921:research/history/logs/agent_action_0081.json:1:{"command":"run","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{i∈S_{e(x)}(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i} + Σ_j γ_j(x) c_j，其中 U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库，C={c_j} 是静态 residual 补偿库。导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的在线链路仍是“trunk 查表 + 单 expert 子库查表 + residual 补偿查表 + 有限加权和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此 `lowrank_expert_residual` 属于扩展兼容。兼容性先筛清楚：`expert_topk` 直接兼容；`lowrank_expert_topk`、`lowrank_expert_residual`、`two_stage_residual_expert`、`factorized_expert_topk` 属扩展兼容；`batch_topk`、`adaptive_budget_topk` 等 batch/sample-coupled family 属不兼容，不能驱动 frontier。r79 与 r80 已连续给出清晰负信号：把 `STAGE1_RATIO` 从 0.25 提到 0.5 会变差，而去掉 low-rank trunk 的 `two_stage_residual_expert` 也明显弱于 matched `lowrank_expert_residual`，说明当前低到中成本带里 trunk 仍是必要组成，且更强 residual cleanup 比更高 expert-stage 预算更重要。相对 r76 仅把 `TRUNK_RANK` 从 32 降到 24，在保持 `ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_residual`、`K=128`、`NUM_EXPERTS=64`、`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`OPTIMIZER=adam`、`LR=8e-4` 和其余训练配方不变时，直接回答当前最关键的低成本问题：既然 routed-only、shared-basis、stage split、以及 trunk-free staged 路线都未带来更优结构段，那么 `lowrank + expert + residual` 这条当前最强兼容主线还能否仅通过进一步压缩必要 trunk 宽度，在保持大部分质量的同时把 total_cost 再往左推一小段，并形成比 r76 更经济的新 Pareto 点。","summary":"Round 81 不再继续切 family，也不回到已给出负信号的 routed-only、shared-basis 或 trunk-free staged 线；而是回到当前最强兼容三段式主线做一次高信息量成本压缩 probe。以 r76 为 reference，只把 `TRUNK_RANK` 从 32 降到 24，直接测试 low-rank trunk 的最小必要宽度是否还能再压，从而在低到中成本带建立更靠左的 `lowrank_expert_residual` 前沿点。","change_type":"param_only","expected_win":"lower_cost","family_name":"lowrank_expert_residual","family_stage":"mainline","self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r76 只改 `TRUNK_RANK`。这比继续在 `lowrank_expert_residual` 上扫 `STAGE1_RATIO`、回到 `expert_topk`/`factorized_expert_topk`，或继续展开 `two_stage_residual_expert` 更符合当前证据，因为最近四轮已经分别否定了 shared-basis、routed-only lookup-budget、higher stage1 budget、以及 trunk-free staged 这四条解释；现在最值得回答的是当前主线里必要 trunk 宽度到底还能压多少。选择 24 而不是直接跳到 16，是为了先做一次更平滑的左移 probe，降低把 trunk 压过头而导致结论只剩“明显变差”的风险。","needs_sanity":false,"env_overrides":[{"key":"TRUNK_RANK","value":"24"}],"touched_files":[],"notes_to_memory":["`lowrank_expert_residual` 的 LUTurbo 形式仍是静态 trunk 库 + 静态 expert 子库 + 静态 residual 补偿库上的有限加权和，兼容性为扩展兼容。","r79 证明把更多预算分给 expert stage 会变差，r80 证明去掉 low-rank trunk 的 trunk-free staged 结构也明显更弱，因此当前主线的下一关键问题是 trunk 宽度还能压多少，而不是继续换 family 或调 budget split。","本轮相对 r76 只改 `TRUNK_RANK=24`，是在 `K=128 / NUM_EXPERTS=64 / STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` recipe 上做成本左移 probe，而不是 old-family 的局部 K 轴细扫。","按当前 cost proxy 代码路径估算，`lowrank_expert_residual K=128 TRUNK_RANK=24 NUM_EXPERTS=64 STAGE1_RATIO=0.25` 仍显著低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束，并应比 r76 进一步降低 encoder 与 deployment 中与 trunk 相关的成本。"],"next_hypotheses":["如果 `TRUNK_RANK=24` 仅小幅伤害 FVU 或接近 r76，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `TRUNK_RANK=16`，确认这条三段式低成本前沿的最小可用 trunk 宽度。","如果 `TRUNK_RANK=24` 反而明显恶化，则可较清晰判定当前 target 上 `TRUNK_RANK=32` 已接近这条主线在低成本带的最小必要 trunk，后续应把预算转向别的兼容 family 或重新考虑更高信息量的新结构。","如果结果接近但不明确，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 `K=160`，判断在确认 trunk 必要宽度后，这条三段式结构是否更适合沿 deployment 侧而不是 trunk 侧继续扩展。"],"reference_round":76}
/root/sparsify-ascend/research/history/logs/agent_round_0105.stdout.log:11922:research/history/round_summaries/round_0090.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u4e3a x_hat = \u03a3_{e\u2208E(z(x))} \u03a3_{i\u2208S_e(z(x))} \u03b1_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}\uff0c\u5176\u4e2d z(x)=Bx \u662f\u5171\u4eab\u4f4e\u7ef4\u6295\u5f71\uff0cE(z) \u662f\u8f7b\u91cf router \u9009\u51fa\u7684\u5c11\u91cf active experts\uff0cexpert \u5185\u7528\u5c0f\u578b low-rank head A_e z \u505a local scoring/top-k\uff0c{B_e} \u662f\u9759\u6001 expert \u5b50\u5e93\u3002\u5728\u7ebf\u4fa7\u53ef\u76f4\u63a5\u5bfc\u51fa\u4e3a\u201cshared low-rank projection + \u5c11\u91cf\u9759\u6001 expert \u5b50\u5e93\u9009\u62e9 + \u5b50\u5e93\u5185\u67e5\u8868 + \u6709\u9650\u52a0\u6743\u6c42\u548c\u201d\u7684 LUTurbo/Lottable \u63a8\u7406\u94fe\u8def\uff0c\u9759\u6001\u5e93\u4e0d\u968f\u6837\u672c\u52a8\u6001\u751f\u6210\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64 `factorized_expert_topk` \u5c5e\u4e8e\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9\uff1b`batch_topk`\u3001`adaptive_budget_topk` \u7b49 batch/sample-coupled family \u4ecd\u5c5e\u4e0d\u517c\u5bb9\uff0c\u4e0d\u80fd\u9a71\u52a8 frontier\u3002\u552f\u4e00\u4e3b\u5047\u8bbe\uff1a\u76f8\u5bf9 r86 \u4ec5\u628a `ARCHITECTURE` \u4ece `lowrank_expert_topk` \u5207\u5230 `factorized_expert_topk`\uff0c\u5728\u4fdd\u6301 `K=128`\u3001`NUM_EXPERTS=16`\u3001`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`\u3001`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`\u3001`OPTIMIZER=adam`\u3001`LR=8e-4` \u548c\u5176\u4f59\u8bad\u7ec3\u914d\u65b9\u4e0d\u53d8\u65f6\uff0c\u5982\u679c r86 \u7684\u5931\u8d25\u4e3b\u8981\u6765\u81ea full-dim routed scorer \u592a\u91cd\u800c\u4e0d\u662f multi-expert MoE-like \u672c\u8eab\uff0c\u90a3\u4e48 shared-basis expert routing \u5e94\u80fd\u5728\u66f4\u4f4e total_cost \u4e0b\u663e\u8457\u6539\u5584 FVU\uff0c\u5e76\u5728 0.3x \u5de6\u53f3\u6210\u672c\u5e26\u5f62\u6210\u65b0\u7684\u7ed3\u6784\u6027 anchor\u3002\u6309\u5f53\u524d\u6210\u672c\u6a21\u578b\u7c97\u4f30\uff0cselection\u22480.19x\u3001deployment\u22480.12x\u3001total\u22480.31x\uff0c\u4f4e\u4e8e 1.5\u00d7h\u00d7n \u786c\u7ea6\u675f\u3002",
