/root/sparsify-ascend/research/history/logs/agent_round_0105.stdout.log:11936:research/history/logs/agent_action_0093.json:1:{"change_type":"param_only","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ACTIVE_EXPERTS","value":"2"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"expert_topk","family_stage":"stabilize","hypothesis":"最终重构公式保持为 x_hat = Σ_{e∈E(x)} Σ_{i∈S_e(x)} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}，其中 E(x) 是轻量 router 选出的少量 active experts，本轮设 |E(x)|=2；每个 B_e={b_{e,i}} 都是静态 expert 子库，在线侧只做“选 2 个静态子库 + 子库内查表/top-k + 有限加权求和”，可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的查表推理链路，因此 `expert_topk` 属于直接兼容。相对地，`factorized_expert_topk` 只属扩展兼容且最近多轮 matched probe 已稳定偏弱；`batch_topk` / `adaptive_budget_topk` 属不兼容，不能驱动 frontier。唯一主假设是：r69→r73→r74 已证明 routed-only `expert_topk` 在固定 `K=160` 下随 `NUM_EXPERTS` 扩容仍有正收益，但当前仍只激活单 expert，尚未回答“容量饱和点是否其实受 active path 过短限制”。相对 r74 只将 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS: 1 -> 2`，若当前瓶颈是单 token 只能访问一个子库，那么在保持 router 很轻且总形式仍为静态子库有限和的前提下，FVU 应明显低于 0.1243，并在约 total_cost=0.69x（selection≈0.53x，deployment≈0.16x）的可行带内形成新的 MoE-like 结构锚点。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` 明显优于 r74，并把 FVU 压到约 0.11 或更低，下一轮保持 `expert_topk` family 不变，只改 `K=128`，测试能否把这条新结构锚点左移回更低部署成本。","如果 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` 只有很弱改善或被 0.49x 附近现有前沿轻易支配，应收缩 routed-only multi-expert active-path 方向，后续把预算转回 `lowrank_expert_residual` 或 `two_stage_residual_expert`。","如果 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` 有改善但成本斜率偏陡，下一轮只改 `NUM_EXPERTS=64`，区分收益来自多 expert 聚合本身还是必须依赖极大的总静态容量。"],"notes_to_memory":["`ACTIVE_EXPERTS` 的 override/persistence 链路已在 r86 完成真实训练验证，因此本轮不需要再做接线修复或参数生效确认轮。","`factorized_expert_topk` 在 r90-r92 的 matched multi-expert probe 上稳定停在约 FVU=0.2158，说明 shared-basis scorer 这条线当前优先级应下调，不值得继续占用低成本探索预算。","按当前 1024x4096 cost proxy 直接实例化估算，`expert_topk K=160 EF=1 NUM_EXPERTS=128 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2` 的成本约为 selection 0.53x、deployment 0.16x、total 0.69x，满足 1.5×h×n 硬约束，也落在允许建立结构性 anchor 的 0.3x-0.8x 带内。"],"reference_round":74,"self_review":"满足单轮单变量约束：相对 r74 只改 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS`。这不是回到 plain selector 或旧 family 的 K/LR 邻域，而是对当前最干净、直接兼容、且已经显示容量正信号的 routed-only MoE-like family 做一次高信息量结构 probe。主要风险是成本会从 r74 的约 0.44x 抬到约 0.69x；如果 FVU 仍不能明显低于当前 <0.5x 前沿的 0.112-0.124 区间，这条 active-path 扩展线就应及时止损。","summary":"不继续重复 `factorized_expert_topk` 的 matched 对照，也不回到旧 family 的局部 K 轴。以 r74 为 reference，只加 `ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`，直接回答 routed-only `expert_topk` 的下一步关键结构问题：当前收益瓶颈到底在总容量，还是在每个 token 只看一个 expert 的过短 active path。","touched_files":[]}
/root/sparsify-ascend/research/history/logs/agent_round_0105.stdout.log:11937:research/history/round_summaries/round_0092.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u4e3a x_hat = \u03a3_{e\u2208E(z(x))} \u03a3_{i\u2208S_e(z(x))} \u03b1_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}\uff0c\u5176\u4e2d z(x)=Bx \u662f\u5171\u4eab\u4f4e\u7ef4\u6295\u5f71\uff0cE(z) \u662f\u8f7b\u91cf router \u9009\u51fa\u7684\u5c11\u91cf active experts\uff0cexpert \u5185\u7528\u5c0f\u578b low-rank head A_e z \u505a local scoring/top-k\uff0c{B_e} \u662f\u9759\u6001 expert \u5b50\u5e93\u3002\u5728\u7ebf\u4fa7\u53ef\u5bfc\u51fa\u4e3a\u201cshared low-rank projection + \u5c11\u91cf\u9759\u6001 expert \u5b50\u5e93\u9009\u62e9 + \u5b50\u5e93\u5185\u67e5\u8868 + \u6709\u9650\u52a0\u6743\u6c42\u548c\u201d\u7684 LUTurbo/Lottable \u63a8\u7406\u94fe\u8def\uff0c\u9759\u6001\u5e93\u4e0d\u968f\u6837\u672c\u52a8\u6001\u751f\u6210\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64 `factorized_expert_topk` \u5c5e\u4e8e\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9\uff1b`expert_topk` \u5c5e\u4e8e\u76f4\u63a5\u517c\u5bb9\uff1b`batch_topk`\u3001`adaptive_budget_topk` \u7b49 batch/sample-coupled family \u4ecd\u5c5e\u4e0d\u517c\u5bb9\uff0c\u4e0d\u80fd\u9a71\u52a8 frontier\u3002\u552f\u4e00\u4e3b\u5047\u8bbe\uff1a\u76f8\u5bf9 r86 \u4ec5\u628a `ARCHITECTURE` \u4ece `lowrank_expert_topk` \u5207\u5230 `factorized_expert_topk`\uff0c\u5728\u4fdd\u6301 `K=128`\u3001`NUM_EXPERTS=16`\u3001`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`\u3001`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`\u3001`OPTIMIZER=adam`\u3001`LR=8e-4` \u548c\u5176\u4f59\u8bad\u7ec3\u914d\u65b9\u4e0d\u53d8\u65f6\uff0c\u5982\u679c r86 \u7684\u5931\u8d25\u4e3b\u8981\u6765\u81ea full-dim routed scorer \u592a\u91cd\u800c\u4e0d\u662f multi-expert MoE-like \u672c\u8eab\uff0c\u90a3\u4e48 shared-basis expert routing \u5e94\u80fd\u5728\u66f4\u4f4e total_cost \u4e0b\u663e\u8457\u6539\u5584 FVU\uff0c\u5e76\u5728\u7ea6 0.3x \u6210\u672c\u5e26\u5f62\u6210\u65b0\u7684\u7ed3\u6784\u6027 anchor\u3002\u6309\u5f53\u524d\u6210\u672c\u6a21\u578b\u7c97\u4f30\uff0cselection\u22480.19x\u3