/root/sparsify-ascend/research/history/logs/agent_round_0105.stdout.log:12008:research/history/logs/agent_action_0085.json:1:{"change_type":"edit_sae_code","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ACTIVE_EXPERTS","value":"2"}],"expected_win":"explore_unknown","experiment_tier":"full","family_name":"lowrank_expert_topk","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"最终重构公式为 x_hat = Σ_{r=1..R} β_r(x) u_r + Σ_{e∈E(x-t(x))} Σ_{i∈S_e(x-t(x))} α_{e,i}(x) b_{e,i}，其中 t(x)=Σ_r β_r(x)u_r，U={u_r} 是静态 low-rank trunk 向量库，{B_e} 是静态 expert 子库，|E(x-t(x))|=ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2。在线导出仍是“trunk 查表 + 2 个静态 expert 子库查表 + 有限加权求和”，静态库不随样本动态生成，因此兼容性判断为扩展兼容。相对 r60 仅新增 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2，在保持 ARCHITECTURE=lowrank_expert_topk、K=128、TRUNK_RANK=64、NUM_EXPERTS=32、EXPANSION_FACTOR=1、OPTIMIZER=adam、LR=8e-4 不变时，验证 shared trunk + routed experts 是否能通过更短于全容量扩张的 active path 提供新的 0.3x-0.8x total_cost Pareto 段。按当前成本模型估算，该点约为 encoder 0.54x、deployment 0.19x、total 0.73x，低于 1.5×h×n 硬约束。","needs_sanity":false,"next_hypotheses":["如果 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2 在约 0.73x total_cost 下显著优于 r60，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 NUM_EXPERTS=64，验证“更大总容量 + 短 active path”是否继续成立。","如果 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2 改善很弱或退化，则下一轮保持 family 不变，只改 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=3 或回到 1，明确当前 target 的最优 active-expert 数，而不是继续混扫旧轴。","如果 lowrank_expert_topk 的多 expert active path 仍不给正信号，则后续把已接通的 ACTIVE_EXPERTS 转去 lowrank_expert_residual，测试 residual cleanup 是否比纯 routed topk 更需要多 expert。"],"notes_to_memory":["ACTIVE_EXPERTS 已完成最小必要接线：sparsify 配置/前向消费、override_registry、config_resolution、runner/runtime 持久化、audit/rebuild、scripts/autoresearch_test.sh 透传均已补齐。","expert_topk、factorized_expert_topk、lowrank_expert_topk、lowrank_expert_residual、two_stage_residual_expert 已本地 smoke 通过 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2 的 forward/backward。","参数生效已验证：本地 validation run 的 checkpoint config.json 与 layer cfg.json 中都出现 active_experts=2；模拟的 round config 也解析出 active_experts=2。","当前 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2 的 lowrank_expert_topk 成本估算约 total 0.73x，属于允许的中低成本结构性 anchor，而不是超预算点。"],"reference_round":60,"self_review":"这轮先修复了 r84 的真实 blocker，而不是把 override 拒绝误判成结构结论。相对 r60 的实际实验语义仍只新增一个 env 参数 ACTIVE_EXPERTS，因此归因保持单变量；代码改动也限制在允许范围内的 sparsify/、research/AutoResearch/、scripts/autoresearch_test.sh。主要风险是 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2 会把 active expert scorer 成本从单 expert 提高到双 expert，total_cost 从约 0.48x 抬到约 0.73x；如果 FVU 改善不足，这条 MoE-like active-path 扩展线就应尽快收缩。","summary":"已修复 ACTIVE_EXPERTS 的端到端接线并完成本地验证，现在可以重跑原本被 r84 阻塞的最小 MoE-like probe。建议本轮以 r60 为 reference，只加 ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2，直接回答 lowrank_expert_topk 的 multi-expert active path 是否值得继续。","touched_files":["sparsify/config.py","sparsify/__main__.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py","research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py","research/AutoResearch/config_resolution.py","research/AutoResearch/runner.py","research/AutoResearch/rebuild_runtime_state.py","research/AutoResearch/controller.py","research/AutoResearch/policy.py","research/AutoResearch/prompt.py","research/AutoResearch/audit_history_execution.py","scripts/autoresearch_test.sh"]}
/root/sparsify-ascend/research/history/logs/agent_round_0105.stdout.log:12010:research/history/round_summaries/round_0072.json:19:    "hypothesis": "\u6700\u7ec8\u91cd\u6784\u516c\u5f0f\u4fdd\u6301\u4e3a x_hat = \u03a3_{i\u2208S_{e(h(x))}(h(x))} \u03b1_{e,i}(h(x)) b_{e,i}\uff0c\u5176\u4e2d h(x)=ReLU(Bx) \u662f\u5171\u4eab basis \u6295\u5f71\uff0ce(h(x)) \u662f\u8f7b\u91cf router \u9009\u51fa\u7684\u5355\u4e2a expert\uff0c{b_{e,i}} \u662f\u9759\u6001 expert \u5b50\u5e93\u539f\u5b50\u3002\u5bfc\u51fa\u5230 LUTurbo/Lottable \u7684\u5728\u7ebf\u94fe\u8def\u4ecd\u662f\u201c\u5171\u4eab\u6295\u5f71 -> router \u9009\u5355\u4e2a\u9759\u6001 expert \u5b50\u5e93 -> expert \u5185 local top-k -> \u9759\u6001\u5e93\u6709\u9650\u52a0\u6743\u548c\u201d\uff0c\u9759\u6001\u5e93\u672c\u8eab\u4e0d\u968f\u6837\u672c\u52a8\u6001\u751f\u6210\uff0c\u56e0\u6b64 `factorized_expert_topk` \u5c5e\u4e8e\u6269\u5c55\u517c\u5bb9\u3002\u76f8\u5bf9 r71 \u4ec5\u628a `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM` \u63d0\u5230 1024\uff0c\u5728\u4fdd\u6301 `ARCHITECTURE=factorized_expert_topk`\u3001`K=160`\u3001`NUM_EXPERTS=32`\u3001`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1` \u548c\u8bad\u7ec3 recipe \u4e0d\u53d8\u65f6\uff0c\u505a\u4e00\u6b21 shared-basis \u5bbd\u5ea6\u4e0a\u9650 probe\uff1a\u5982\u679c r71 \u7684\u5931\u8d25\u4e3b\u8981\u6765\u81ea\u5171\u4eab\u4f4e\u79e9 basis \u8fc7\u7a84\u800c\u4e0d\u662f\u7ed3\u6784\u672c\u8eab\u9519\u8bef\uff0c\u5219\u66f4\u5bbd\u7684 basis \u5e94\u660e\u663e\u538b\u4f4e FVU\uff1b\u5982\u679c\u5373\u4f7f\u63a5\u8fd1 full-width basis \u4ecd\u660e\u663e\u843d\u540e\uff0c\u5219\u53ef\u4ee5\u8f83\u5e72\u51c0\u5730\u628a\u5f53\u524d `expert-internal low-rank` \u539f\u578b\u5f52\u6863\uff0c\u4e0d\u518d\u8ba9\u5b83\u7ee7\u7eed\u5360\u7528\u4e3b\u7ebf\u9884\u7b97\u3002",
