xpert`，避免后续 resume 校验静默漏掉该参数。"],"reference_round":104,"self_review":"这轮先修复了 r105 的真实 blocker，而不是把 `Disallowed env override keys: LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 误判成结构结论。相对 r104 的实验语义仍只新增一个 env 参数 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT`，满足单变量原则；代码改动也限制在允许范围内的 `sparsify/`、`research/AutoResearch/`、`scripts/autoresearch_test.sh`。我已做本地验证，确认新 key 进入 override allowlist、runner runtime config、checkpoint config 和 resume signature，不会在训练启动前再次被判为 disallowed。","summary":"已实际落盘 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT` 的端到端接线，并完成本地验证：新参数可被 AutoResearch 接受，expert family 可消费该宽度，`shared_routed_expert_topk` 的 round config / checkpoint config 都能正确记录 `latents_per_expert=512`。建议本轮以 r104 为 reference，只加 `LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=512`，先拿到“更窄 per-expert width”这条 high-information low-cost 方向的首个有效训练点。","touched_files":["sparsify/__main__.py","sparsify/config.py","sparsify/sparse_coder.py","research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py","research/AutoResearch/config_resolution.py","research/AutoResearch/controller.py","research/AutoResearch/policy.py","research/AutoResearch/prompt.py","research/AutoResearch/runner.py","research/AutoResearch/rebuild_runtime_state.py","research/AutoResearch/audit_history_execution.py","scripts/autoresearch_test.sh"]}
